Paradise Fruit Co Inc said itsboard declared a dividend of 25 cts per share, payable March 31to holders of record March 19.    The company last paid 50 cts per share in January 1986 andbefore that paid 60 cts in January 1985.    Paradise said commercial bank lending agreements it enteredinto in June 1986 include retained earnings requirements thatlimit the amount of earnings available for distribution toshareholders. Reuter&#3;